*** Settings ***
Library    RequestsLibrary
Library    Collections

*** Variables ***
${BASE_URL}          http://127.0.0.1:8000
${LATEST_RESPONSE}   ${None}

*** Keywords ***
Submit A Valid Payment Request
    # Source: POST /v1/payment — API doc section 3.1
    Create Session    api    ${BASE_URL}
    ${payload}=    Create Dictionary    amount=100    currency=VND
    ${response}=    POST On Session    api    /v1/payment    json=${payload}
    Status Should Be    200    ${response}
    Set Test Variable    ${LATEST_RESPONSE}    ${response}

Verify Payment Response Is Successful
    # Source: POST /v1/payment — Expected 200 response schema
    ${json}=    Set Variable    ${LATEST_RESPONSE.json()}
    Should Be Equal    ${json['status']}    SUCCESS
